MarkyVigoroth
[[Image:Magnemite.jpg|right|thumb|MarkyVigoroth's crap artwork.]]

MarkyVigoroth is a 14 year-old retarded [[Christian]] [[furry]] from black person. He is also a member of [[deviantART]], where he posts his drawings that look like they were made by an armadillo on speed. Like most Christians, he thinks that [[homosexuals]] are evil and will go to [[hell]]. His fursona is a Christian [[Pokemon|Vigoroth]]. He says that at one time, he wanted to experiment with him by drawing him in all the the "good" styles (i.e. [[sick fuck|inflation]], muscle) (What he means by "good" styles, he means non-adult, like [[pornography]] and [[fetish]]; those styles are so not good from a Christian like him). He does not realize that inflation is a fetish. But he probably finds it sexy and just doesn't want to ruin his image.

Marky is friends with [[Hhhippo]], who is considerably fucked up and thinks that being a fat-ass [[lie|is sexy]]. But don't worry. If you are at least a fairly decent artist Marky will pay you a visit after visit until you become his best friend on the whole world. He will give you tons of his shitty art and expect something of a better quality in return and don't you dare deny him or you will burn in [[hell]]! 

Despite his art looking like [[shit]], he uploads it anyway for the whole [[internets]] to see.

